西瓦鹿外觀像現今的[[霍加狓|霍加狓]]，但體型較大及粗壯，[[肩|肩]]高達{{convert|2.2|m|ft|abbr=on}}，總高度可達{{convert|3|m|ft|abbr=on}}，體重則可達{{convert|400|-|500|kg|abbr=on}}。一個更新的估計顯示西瓦鹿的體重可能重達{{convert|1250|kg|abbr=on}}<ref name=":0">{{cite journal | url = http://rsbl.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/12/1/20150940 | title = The extinct, giant giraffid ''Sivatherium giganteum'': skeletal reconstruction and body mass estimation | journal = [[生物學報|生物學報]] | date = January 2016 | volume = 12 | issue = 1 | doi = 10.1098/rsbl.2015.0940 | first1 = Christopher | last1 = Basu | first2 = Peter L. | last2 = Falkingham | first3 = John R. | last3 = Hutchinson | access-date = 2018-10-11 | archive-date = 2018-10-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181011172921/http://rsbl.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/12/1/20150940 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，這讓西瓦鹿成為目前已知最大型的[[反芻動物|反芻動物]]，此估計體重不含雄性鹿角的重量，因此實際體重可能更重。牠有一對很闊的[[鹿角|鹿角]]，[[眼睛|眼睛]]上則有第二對鹿角。牠的肩膀非常強壯，可以支撐[[頸部|頸部]][[肌肉|肌肉]]及重的[[頭顱骨|頭顱骨]]<ref name=EoDP>{{cite book |editor-last=Palmer | editor-first = D. | date = 1999 |title= The Marshall Illustrated Encyclopedia of Dinosaurs and Prehistoric Animals|publisher= Marshall Editions|location=London|page= 278|isbn= 1-84028-152-9}}</ref>。

